Lob,Address,Verification,API,is,a,fee,based,cloud,API,that,verifies,addresses,to,confirm,deliverability,potential,This,API,performs,cleansing,standardizing,and,local,geocoding,of,submitted,addresses,both,domestic,and,foreign,The,Lob,Address,Verification,API,supports,UTF,encoded,characters,to,ensure,worldwide,verification,ability,Domestic,verification,is,free,and,verification,of,over,countries,is,available,through,a,fee,Lob,API,requires,an,authentication,key,and,is,REST,oriented,This,API,provides,Ruby,Node,js,PHP,Java,Python,wrappers,for,ease,of,integration